------------------------------------------------------------------------------
HELP ATTACH
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ATTACH EDITOR [EDITORNAME]

    This command allows to use extern editor-programs. To use the standard
    PARROT-editor use ATTACH EDITOR without argument.

    At this time the only external editor available is the fullscreen editor
    uemacs.ttp.

    Because there is NO help available inside the editor, read help UEMACS.HLP
    BEFORE using uemacs!!

    ACCESS:   CLASS 01

